    "body": "## What's New in v1.1.0\n\n### Features\n- Automatic updates via Sparkle\n- Notarized for macOS security\n- Available via Homebrew\n\n### Installation\n\n**Direct Download:**\n1. Download `DeeplinkScout.dmg`\n2. Open the DMG and drag DeeplinkScout to Applications\n3. Launch from Applications folder\n\n**Homebrew:**\n```bash\n# Tap the repository\nbrew tap DominatorVbN/DeeplinkScout\n\n# Install DeeplinkScout\nbrew install deeplinkscout\n```\n\nOr in a single command:\n```bash\nbrew install DominatorVbN/deeplinkscout/deeplinkscout\n```\n\n### Requirements\n- macOS 14.6 (Sonoma) or later\n- Xcode command line tools\n\n---\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/DominatorVbN/DeeplinkScoutApp/compare/previous-tag...v1.1.0\n"
